{"tid":1760893,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"派4000派到pat 屎咁，依家960萬幾快就比到出去","createTime":"2019-11-28T13:54:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-28T17:02:30.000Z","uid":57012,"like":23,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"9e5b270228012e027f145b7e47f53bbf26db9fe3","tid":1760893,"uid":57012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T13:54:03.000Z","msg":"政府接納賑災基金諮詢委員會的建議，從賑災基金批出兩項共960萬7千元的撥款，予兩間機構賑濟印度比哈爾邦水災災民。<br />\n<br />\n政府發言人表示，印度比哈爾邦水災的受災人數超過2百萬人。兩項撥款分別為510萬8千元予香港仁人家園及449萬9千元予國際培幼會（香港）。撥款會用於提供臨時居所包、食水包和廚具包，以及家庭和衞生用品，約5萬8千多名災民受惠。兩間救援機構將會進行賑災的地點並不相同，並沒有資源重疊。委員會希望撥款為災民提供適切援助，幫助他們早日回復正常生活。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔係話救災唔岩<br />\n<br />\n不過<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">自己地方d民生議題都未搞掂，憑咩理人地d事</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1495004-20191128.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1495004-20191128.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=gSA20A4kU26EBUHkB65AtK0EM2ZTCgB2Df5M2YAuo3Y%3D&h=498b626d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1495004-20191128.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=626664a1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1495004-20191128.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"d16599a53977008e615d330129db833420be26f0","tid":1760893,"uid":57012,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T13:55:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ufi6q1e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUfi6q1e.jpg&h=95ee5785&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XVdx51f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXVdx51f.jpg&h=262259cf&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0b34f570ecabbaeb82642868888ed84b341b9a82","tid":1760893,"uid":57012,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T14:01:39